Betrayed by his disciple and friends, the Immortal Emperor died in grief, just like that. Though his mortal body may be dead, his soul spirit lives on. With the [Emperors Scripture], a precious treasure, he aims to get revenge. Luo Wuji has returned to Earth, ready to seek revenge on his foes and rebuild his godhood! In this life, the name Wuji shall surpass everything, even the whole universe!
(Source: Bilibili Comics)

The genius lawyer No Hyeong-Jin's justice-executing returner fantasy! Valedictorian of his University, perfect score on the Bar Exam, and even a 95% case win rate. No Hyeong-Jin was a so-called successful lawyer! While he was fighting against evil, higher powers to make South Korea a just and fair land, he was ruthlessly murdered by National Intelligence Service agents. "He shouldn't have died..." No Hyeong-Jin was a man sent by Emperor Yeom-Ra to fix corruption on Earth! However, after ending up in hell without having been able to achieve anything, Emperor Yeom-Ra returns No Hyeong-Jin back in time... What is this "power" given to him by Emperor Yeom-Ra? Will No Hyeong-Jin be able to change his future as well as the future of South-Korea?! (Source: KakaoPage, translated)
